headline: Humana Incurs Q4 Loss, Revenues Up Y/Y on CenterWell Unit Strength
summary: HUM incurs a wider year-over-year loss in Q4 due to rising costs, weaker investment income and membership declines. Yet, revenues climb 12% on CenterWell strength.

headline: 1 Safe-and-Steady Stock with Exciting Potential and 2 We Brush Off
summary: A stock with low volatility can be reassuring, but it doesn’t always mean strong long-term performance. Investors who prioritize stability may miss out on higher-reward opportunities elsewhere.
